title: Russia Outmaneuvers US in Syria, Dealing Blow to Washington's Credibility
text: Moscow's decision to provide military assistance to Damascus is a win-win for Russia: if it succeeds, Russia ensures its leadership; if it fails, the blame will rest on Washington and the West for not joining Russia's anti-ISIL coalition, Armenian-Russian expert Andranik Migranyan deems. ...
